title: Ranked Queues dont open at 10:00
body: At 10:00 this morning in NZ time ranked queues werent open. My friend computer and online time both said it was 10:00 but ranked queues didint come up for another 10 seconds or so. In my opinion this is just slack by Riot and needs to be dealth with.

replies.body:
Maybe your clock is 10 seconds early?
Or you could be a time traveller.
Or it could just not matter.
It's 10:00 Sydney time, not NZ time, NZ in ahead in time, so you know..
